name: After Hours pt.2
description:
After Hours pt.2 

Joyo packed all the records and he was ready to go home. The night was a bit windy than usual, he was starving and he can see Tina next to him looks pale and hungry, she always hungry at this hour... 

This lover boy was so happy to finally on his way holding a record shop with his long time crush, Tina. They used to work at the same office but Tina just resign last week. Joyo also have plans to resign but not yet... he must find another job replecement first with higher salary of course, since the shop just a month old and he needed the money to pay the bills and everything. 

Joyo Sapta, that's how his parents named him. They raised him very well, you can count on Joyo anytime and he always be there, Joyo have a younger brother, Joni. They both shared the same place to stay, since their parents live in another town. Good thing, Joyo always can count on Joni to help a little with the shop, when he still at work. 

The night was getting late, Joyo wrapped things up and he went straight to the nearest mini market to grab some instant cup noodles. He thought Tina might want take them home.


00:36 seconds 1080x1080p animated drawings with audio sampled beats and original tunes by Sartje.
